Output demo/out/ui-upload-progress.gif

Require bash

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 960
Set Height 340
Set TypingSpeed 10 ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 20

Type "$HOVEL_DEMO_UI_BIN show upload-progress --width 96 --frames 8 --delay 45ms"
Enter
Wait+Screen /uploaded mock-survey-report.json/
Sleep 2000 ms
